o our big Stories of the Season event on Friday night. A packed house, and =
I met tons of nice readers and awards voters at the reception, though if I=
=E2=80=99m honest, the special =E2=80=9CWhat I=E2=80=99m Drinking=E2=80=9D =
cocktail was gross (I hate Campari). We=E2=80=99ll post videos of the panel=
s throughout the season, and our keynotes Denis Villeneuve (Dune: Part Two)=
 and Mikey Madison (Anora) will be on The Town this week. Thanks to the fan=
tastic Puck events team and our sponsors Polestar, Wondery, HBO and Max, an=
d Mayer Brown.

